         <t:abstract><t:p><t:foreign xml:lang="gez">Dǝrsān wa-tǝmhǝrt za-ʾabawina ḥawāryāt qǝddusān</t:foreign> is a collection of nine texts transmitted as part of
         either <t:ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1544Gebrah">Gǝbra Ḥǝmāmāt</t:ref> or <t:ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2382Taamme">Taʾammǝra ʾIyasus</t:ref>.
